---
title: Gnocchi Bake with Courgette, Mushrooms & Sage and Rocket Salad
description: Pan-frying gnocchi brings a whole extra dimension to these pillowy little dumplings. The golden, crispy exterior provides a beautiful contrast with today's creamy sauce.
